          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex> be <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-000U.xml" title="Biinverse" addr="//erct/erct-000U" type="local">biinvertible</fr:link>; then for any type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex>, the precomposition map <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen -\circ  f\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\colon  
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen B\to  C\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\to 
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen A\to  C\right \rparen \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-000U.xml" title="Biinverse" addr="//erct/erct-000U" type="local">biinvertible</fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
